      <div type="edition" xml:lang="okz-Latn">
        <p><lb n="1"></lb><gap quantity="3" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap><num value="7">7</num> śaka pūrṇṇamī khneta phālguṇa saura<lb break="no" n="2"></lb><supplied reason="lost">vāra</supplied> <gap quantity="2" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> mvaya thmā thṅgaiya gi nu vraḥ yanapati pa <lb n="3"></lb><gap quantity="2" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> thvāya caṁnāṁ kālpanā nu bhūmi ti jauva cu<lb break="no" n="4"></lb><supplied reason="lost">ña</supplied> Aṁvi nā lvek ta khloña travāṅa raṁcyeka pradhāna <lb n="5"></lb>sruka nu gvena sgoṅa gi sre nu caṁ n<seg subtype="vowel" type="component">
            <gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="component"></gap>
          </seg><gap quantity="1" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap><seg subtype="body" type="component">
            <gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="component"></gap>
          </seg>ai jā viddhi n<unclear>e</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ḥ</supplied> <lb n="6"></lb><gap quantity="1" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> thvāya ta vraḥ pāda kamrateṅa Aña śrīdharan<supplied reason="lost">ī</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"></lb>ndravarmmadeva jā vraḥ rājadhārmma caṁ tvaṅa mvaya teṁ <lb n="8"></lb>caṁnāṁ kālpanā ta gi nā saṅkrānta raṅka liḥ <num value="5">5</num> qva<lb break="no" n="9"></lb>ra <num value="2">2</num> striya pamasa vraḥ gandha tarāpa <gap quantity="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"></gap> ta gi <g type="dotMid">.</g> te<lb break="no" n="10"></lb>ṅ saṁ teṅa traiya teṅa gaṅa puruṣa ta paṁmre <lb n="11"></lb>saṅkrānta loña siddhakaryya loña prāṁ vasa<lb break="no" n="12"></lb>na neḥ nā khneta <g type="circle">.</g> nā pakṣa rṇṇoca raṅka caṁnāṁ <lb n="13"></lb>nā saṅkrānta liḥ <num value="5">5</num> qvara <num value="2">2</num> striya pamasa vraḥ <lb n="14"></lb>gandha teṅa ratna teṅ sudhivasa puruṣa ta paṁ<lb break="no" n="15"></lb> mre saṅkrānta loña vau loña caṁ qva <lb n="16"></lb>loña nila loña janpada <g type="circle">.</g> qnak ta taṅa <lb n="17"></lb>neḥ phoṅa nuv· nā kalpananā t<choice>
            <unclear>a</unclear>
            <unclear>i</unclear>
          </choice> kamra<lb break="no" n="18"></lb>teṅa <choice>
            <orig>j</orig>
            <reg>ja</reg>
          </choice>g<choice>
            <orig>ā</orig>
            <reg>a</reg>
          </choice>t ta gi <add place="below">ta</add> paripālna nau ru qnaka ta <lb n="19"></lb>la<gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"></gap> kalpanā ta roḥ neḥ phoṅa ta <lb n="20"></lb>kamrateṅ <choice>
            <orig>j</orig>
            <reg>ja</reg>
          </choice>g<choice>
