          </choice>ta śivapūra neḥ Aṁpāla <lb n="21"></lb>do<gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"></gap> rājakālābhijña<seg subtype="body" type="component">
            <gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="component"></gap>
          </seg>rā<gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"></gap> lvaḥ <lb n="22"></lb>śiva <gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"></gap> tvānta leṅ <seg subtype="body" type="component">
            <gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="component"></gap>
          </seg>yan ta paṅ<gap quantity="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="23"></lb><gap quantity="10" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap></p>
